item.title: CVE-2021-36339|2024-08-04T00:54:51.453Z -- dell -- solutions%20enabler%20vapp
item.description: The Dell EMC Virtual Appliances before 9.2.2.2 contain undocumented user accounts. A local malicious user may potentially exploit this vulnerability to get privileged access to the virtual appliance.
